      <title>美国州长热切希望开发无人机技术以备访台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-governor-eager-to-develop-drone-tech-set-for-taiwan-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国一位州长热衷于在其州建立无人机中心，准备带领一个由行业高管组成的代表团访问台湾——这是双方在该技术领域的合作日益加深的标志。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-governor-eager-to-develop-drone-tech-set-for-taiwan-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 06:32:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其财长西姆塞克在高盛会议上承诺严守财政纪律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/turkey-s-simsek-pledges-fiscal-discipline-in-goldman-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位了解讨论情况的人士透露，土耳其财政部长穆罕默德·西姆塞克在纽约的一次会议上告诉投资者，紧缩的​​财政政策将在通货紧缩过程中发挥决定性作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/turkey-s-simsek-pledges-fiscal-discipline-in-goldman-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 04:18:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国罕见试射洲际弹道导弹 向太平洋展示实力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/china-launches-icbm-with-dummy-warhead-into-pacific-ocean</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国向太平洋发射了一枚洲际弹道导弹，这似乎是中国四十年来首次公开进行此类试验，是在美国召集世界领导人出席联合国大会之际展示军事实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/china-launches-icbm-with-dummy-warhead-into-pacific-ocean</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 03:53:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾军方领导人拒绝暂停部署美国导弹系统 遭中国猛烈抨击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/philippine-military-head-backs-stay-of-us-missile-system-slammed-by-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾军方领导人支持美国在该国永久部署导弹系统，该系统已在该国部署数月，此举不免激怒中国，因为中国曾称这一武器部署“会破坏稳定”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/philippine-military-head-backs-stay-of-us-missile-system-slammed-by-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 03:22:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>名字之争凸显日本领导人竞选的分裂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/fight-over-names-highlights-split-in-japan-s-leadership-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[关于夫妻是否应被允许使用不同姓氏的争论已持续了几十年，如今已成为日本最高职位竞选中最具争议的问题之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/fight-over-names-highlights-split-in-japan-s-leadership-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗总统称期待举行核协议会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/iran-president-says-he-expects-to-hold-meeting-on-nuclear-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统马苏德·佩泽什基安表示，在与法国领导人埃马纽埃尔·马克龙举行“积极”会晤并与中国外交部长举行会谈后，双方正计划讨论搁置多年的核协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/iran-president-says-he-expects-to-hold-meeting-on-nuclear-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 00:49:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
